      "patchset_number": 2,
      "line": 56,
      "message": "BUG! getDataNodes will throw a DataNodeFoundException (versus queryDataNodes which would return empty collection). Add try/catch, or use queryDataNodes instead.\n\nWe really need to get NCMP covered under integration tests.",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 6742,
        "name": "Daniel Hanrahan",
        "display_name": null,
