      "patchset_number": 2,
      "line": 50,
      "message": "What about Toine's suggestion of returning the list of existing subscriptions? We will need that for adding new a subscription.\n\n    boolean isOngoingCmSubscriptions(datastoreType, cmHandleId, xpath) {\n        var existingSubscriptions = getOngoingCmSubscriptions(datastoreType, cmHandleId, xpath);\n        return !existingSubscriptions.isEmpty();\n    }\n\n    Collection<String> getOngoingCmSubscriptions(datastoreType, cmHandleId, xpath) {\n        var existingNodes = cpsQueryService.queryDataNodes(...);\n        if (existingNodes.isEmpty()) {\n            return Collections.emptyList();\n        }\n        return existingNodes.iterator().next().getLeaves().get(\"subscribers\");\n    }",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 6742,
        "name": "Daniel Hanrahan",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "daniel.hanrahan@est.tech",
        "username": "danielhanrahan"
      },
      "updated": "2024-02-09 15:16:12.000000000",
